CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1956, pg. 12 reads: "25th Anniversary - The Rev. and Mrs. Harold R. Tolliver, pastor of Grace Memorial Presbyterian Church, and his wife, admire the 25th anniversary cake, centerpiece of the June 17 celebration ,which honored them for a quarter century of service as pastor and "First Lady" of the church which was his first charge. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Rev. and Mrs. Harold R. Tolliver, cutting three tiered 25th Anniversary cake, in Grace Memorial Presbyterian Church
